      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis integrity under high lateral loads. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides precise gate entry, paired with a factory-spec variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The exterior retains its original deep luster with no paint metered outside factory tolerances, while the interior leather maintains its matte finish and bolster rigidity. A true purist's specimen with zero bushing deflection and a perfectly linear power band.",
